  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 0882748dc185476197f6ec16b90304dd, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  notesText: 'Unity has two main input mechanisms:  "Input" and "InputSystem".


    They
    are transitioning from the older "Input" to the newer "InputSystem", and you
    can probably read lots of internet comments on how each one is terrible or wonderful.


    In
    this sample project, we''re using InputSystem because it runs indpendently from
    the rendering frame rate, and because it will be the officially-supported Unity
    method going forward.

'
